          "date": "2014-07-06 05:39:51.000000000",
          "tz": -420
        },
        "subject": "LU-5163 mdt: using mdo_lookup(..) in mdt_rename_parents_lock()",
        "message": "LU-5163 mdt: using mdo_lookup(..) in mdt_rename_parents_lock()\n\nUsing mdo_lookup() instead of mdo_is_subdir() to check the\nparent/child relationship in mdt_rename_parents_lock(), because\nwe only need to know if source and target directory are direct\nparent and child, otherwise they can not be locked in one\noperation, except rename, but rename has already been serialized\nby global rename lock.\nBesides, in the original implementation, mdo_is_subdir() is not\nprotected by ldlm lock, which might bring some risks.\nChange-Id: I63bb145fc49a892ef0918253d8bacee4f4ebe33c\nSigned-off-by: Wang Di <di.wang@intel.com>\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
  },
